#project description# Smart University Assistant

Backend system built using Flask to handle university-related student queries.

## Current Status
Phase 1: Flask Backend Foundation (In Progress)

## Features Implemented
- Flask server setup
- Basic API routes:
  - `/` – Home route
  - `/health` – Health check
  - `/ask` – Accept student questions (dummy response)

## Tech Stack (Planned)
- Flask (Backend)
- PostgreSQL (Structured data)
- MongoDB (Unstructured data)
- LLM integration
- RAG pipeline

## Project Goal
To build an intelligent assistant capable of answering university queries using structured and unstructured data.

